aria-labelledby.description: An id or space-separated list of ids of elements that label the Toggle.

className.description: Class names applied to the element or a function that returns them based on the component's state.

defaultPressed.description: The default pressed state. Use when the component is not controlled.

onPressedChange.description: Callback fired when the pressed state is changed.

render.description: A function to customize rendering of the component.

value.description:
A unique string that identifies the component when used
inside a ToggleGroup.
